title: Wild Garlic Focaccia | Jamie & Gennaro | #MyFoodMemories | AD
description:
This is a paid AD by Hotpoint. 
Whenever Jamie makes any bread, particularly Focaccia, it reminds him of getting to know his 'London Dad' Gennaro Contaldo. Making this recipe is how they got to know each other and became such close friends. This Wild Garlic Focaccia is incredibly delicious, give it a try and share your story #MyFoodMemories
